The changelog is generated from the PR's title so we remove the changelog section from the PR template.
Add note to inform that clear and meaningful PR title are important.

Remove gitter and add public channel on mattermost (#6322)

Remove the reference to the gitter channel and add link to the public channel on Eclipse's Mattermost.

issue.title: Update version from 5.3 to 5.5?
issue.body:
This repo is currently using version 5.3 of Laravel. How would one go about updating to the latest version of Laravel? Should I literally be copying the contents of https://github.com/laravel/laravel then submit this as a PR?

Thanks!

comment.body: Laravel has upgrade guides that I would follow for making the required changes. Remember, too, that there are some changes in several files to preconfigure the app for Nanobox use, so you'll need to ensure those are intact, too.

issue.title: Add ability to filter yarn cache (fixes #3200)
issue.body: **Summary** This was proposed in #3200. It adds the ability filter the cache list with multiple filters. If it matches any of the filters it will add the module to the list. If it doesn't it just skips. **Test plan** Added tests for this new feature. Matching with single filter: Matching with different filters: No match in the cache:
